Subject: Re: [racket-bug] all/12466: Request a bitmap/file function in 2htdp/image
Date: Thu, 29 Dec 2011 22:19:04 -0600

 Okay, I'll add it.
 
 Yes, there is a way to specify that in Racket, you use define-runtime-path.
 
 I also see now that 'bitmap' only _can_ expand into
 define-runtime-path (or maybe it can't, but it should be able to in
 principle), it doesn't actually do it. :(
 
 Robby
 
