 &gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;<br>
 &gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; *** Description:<br>
 &gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; It would be nice to have a bitmap/file functio=
 n in the 2htdp/image teachpack, since &#39;bitmap&#39; is a macro, it&#39;s=
  not helpful for loading from a file whose name is computed and stored in a=
  variable at runtime. It&#39;s possible to use bitmap/url with a file:// ur=
 l, but that doesn&#39;t seem to be able to do relative paths.<br>
 
